   },
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "A stooped scholar looks up from a wall of salvaged drives. “You’re Awakened. Good. The System tells you what you are. I keep what it edits out.”",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People3",
      "index": 0
     }
    },
    {
     "type": "choice",
     "prompt": "Ask the Archivist:",
     "options": [
      {
       "label": "What is this place?",
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "“The Ashlab. Before the System onlined, people studied the dark beneath Dawnhearth. The OWPS — the Overflow Working Prevention Study. They learned what the Calamity is. Then the System reclassified the lab as ‘property’ and the staff as ‘resolved’.”",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People3",
          "index": 0
         }
        }
       ]
      },
      {
       "label": "The cycle — is it real?",
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "“You feel it, don’t you. The repetition. The names recut on the well. Every Awakened has stood where you stand and asked me this. I answer the same way each time, and forget I’ve answered. The System resets the page. It does not reset the dark.”",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People3",
          "index": 0
         }
        }
       ]
      },
      {
       "label": "How do I get out?",
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "“Not by descending. Descending is what it wants — it feeds. The way out is in what the OWPS buried on the lowest floors. Find their cache. Bring it here. Then we’ll talk about endings.”",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People3",
          "index": 0
         }
        }
       ]
      },
      {
       "label": "Leave",
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "“Come back when the dark has taught you to doubt.”",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People3",
          "index": 0
         }
        }
       ]
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
